“I’m more of a style stylist rather than a fashion stylist. I like personality in outfits, rather than a full head-to-toe runway, even though that’s amazing, too.”

In working with her clients, who’ve included Jessica Alba, Kate Hudson, Yalitza Aparicio and Goldie Hawn, @sophielopez is searching for a “vibe,” an “identity” — whatever it is that makes them human. Link in bio.
